{"tid":1146600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸仔被家長打成香腸嘴　揭中國貧窮農村的悲哀","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T11:26:10.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d80e44fbe94788bd6b7fe8322ed475aa9944d5","tid":1146600,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190509/640_5bf31294f83417ed01f2579f1ab4d7fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190509%2F640_5bf31294f83417ed01f2579f1ab4d7fb.jpg&h=c8da6f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國廣西玉林市有一名12歲男童，被人發現遭到家長打罵，更被打成「香腸嘴」。不過這位男童的故事，也揭露出中國貧窮農村的悲哀。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《北京時間》報導，這名男童被人發現穿著校服，但嘴巴整個被家長打得不成人形，腫成香腸嘴，影片流出後立刻引發關注。警方表示，這名男童來自非常貧窮的農村家庭，父親一個人要養5個小孩和兩位80歲老人。而且男童平時常常離家出走，甚至去偷東西，警方說，農村人脾氣比較「牛」，發現小孩不乖就是打，但警方也表示家長打得有點過頭了，會再好好勸說。<br />\n<br />\n去年底《中國禁聞網》就曾經報導過農村孩子的悲哀，他們的父母必須離鄉背井打工，所以這群孩子在家裡，等於在沒有父母管教的情況下，被迫自力更生長大，或者讓年邁的祖父母撫養，但祖父母已無太多力氣管教孩子。如果女孩子生在保守的農村家庭，那麼她的人生一定是：「上到初中、出去打工、找個老公、奉獻子宮。」在農村，生二胎只是為了要男孩，姐姐成為「扶弟魔」放棄學業去賺錢，女孩在上高中的年紀就出嫁，至今仍然是普遍現象。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"78fd1c8ddede5e449ecafc476f2b861ab27a4aef","tid":1146600,"uid":236414,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"所以鄉下仔永遠都係鄉下仔"},{"pid":"f8ae87e9db690d22ae0047f65b15dc1514c4d323","tid":1146600,"uid":107927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"先讓一部份中國人富起來"},{"pid":"323df7b244b8f49ab3b4b999dcba9d40dccd8a84","tid":1146600,"uid":19609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"買condom 啦仆街"},{"pid":"96a8bc2eea84fed53d1e66c6e7607508b2bf512f","tid":1146600,"uid":55533,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/a3_16044538965a798a24a38c1-1050x494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fa3_16044538965a798a24a38c1-1050x494.jpg&h=90b141d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8543a4e06bf5394be1814a8e1a269737235716da","tid":1146600,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b78b77931b3aca358354ecb9058d3f44887693","tid":1146600,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"支那畜牲咪撚生啦<br />\n死撚晒去啦"},{"pid":"dd7b67e85e353263591ddff7ea92cd70ee914dd1","tid":1146600,"uid":1372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"323df7b244b8f49ab3b4b999dcba9d40dccd8a84","tid":1146600,"uid":19609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"買condom 啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"佢哋又唔係唔小心生咗出嚟，係有心生個仔出嚟養老"},{"pid":"f5e1e215b8d6d72672d706cb0aacb7e8f782dab0","tid":1146600,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"往死裡打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6524599bee1d72a9c1a37667fbf3161f457770","tid":1146600,"uid":204929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"點解好似越窮嘅人係越會主張， <br />\n棒下出孝子呢個道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"}]}